{"tid":950401,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Pro Club part time 球會 Orphanage，專收無波開孤兒仔","createTime":"2018-12-21T13:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T08:45:16.000Z","uid":122,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"a90e4a5420aa3fc995e401da66896ce7c9391f28","tid":950401,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:19:35.000Z","msg":"暫時D3 公開球會，不求成績<br />\n專收死谷/無波開孤兒仔<br />\n<br />\n~如果你怕教練型球員出聲dominate,想靜靜地玩又得,插mic 9up 又得,幾個踢熟左開party 又得<br />\n~唔為比賽,純玩<br />\n~唔理咩巴塞車仔踢法,乜都好,傳中OK但最好準/差唔多<br />\nL1 高波可以,但你見你隊友無跑/無意識跑就算數啦<br />\n~唔鳩扭, 應傳則傳<br />\n~盤扭大師練SM既唔該去drop in <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n~新手老手歡迎,唔好屌人老豆老母,你自己都做過新手,分享下點玩無所謂<br />\n~tg group聯絡 ,自己覺得夠人就開,唔使等人<br />\n~位置先到先得,如果玩左幾場,又見有巴打想換下位, 大家將就下,自律<br />\n~承上最好就多功能撚,最少都識打2個位,唔太識打唔緊要,肯傳比人就得<br />\n~暫時谷內氣氛良好<br />\n<br />\n只踢<br />\n多人舉報行為不儉既痴線佬<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n有興趣留tg<br />\n或者經朋友介紹入group 都得"},{"pid":"46232b46088004e998b278bd344e839b247e6acc","tid":950401,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T17:24:14.000Z","msg":"D2"},{"pid":"947da86bea8cfe42f06c7ce4ac4bcd108e4ba3dd","tid":950401,"uid":29781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T08:27:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/heioocc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fheioocc&d=Hr6YcpbB53ZKSqCYDQqOFARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=db9c6c27\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/heioocc</a>"},{"pid":"8b227982ef939727ac665e68b4f2e419a8e73bde","tid":950401,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T01:04:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf507fb726f62d9045ca8870e7922733e759e36","tid":950401,"uid":79385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T02:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaecf8d5195669bbe184202a1cde8b1e9